Controllers

Class ControllerGame

  • java.lang.Object
    • Controllers.ControllerGame

  • public class ControllerGame
extends java.lang.Object
    The class ControllerGame is the home page after logging in. It only displays different buttons such as starting a game, log out or show profile page.
